1. Install boost
   sudo yum install boost*.

2. Install libconfig
   sudo yum install libconfig.
   
3. Install libxs
   tar zxvf libxs-1.2.0.tar.gz
   cd libxs-1.2.0
   ./configure
   make 
   sudo make install
   
Declaration:
Theron is a C++ actor mode library, it's written by Ashton Mason, this is the introduction of Mason(https://www.linkedin.com/in/ashtonmason). And the theron homepage is http://www.theron-library.com/. For convenient, I directly use some .h files and lib in my project. 